node.text: Beauty is in the eye of the beholder... so who do you see? In this time of racial unrest, we need to change the way we see Blackness: it’s value, it’s diversity, it’s depth, it’s history, it’s potential. Let’s open our eyes and see beyond the superficial biases that we have, and gain a deeper appreciation because #BlackLivesMatter

node.title: @badassboz : Seeing BEAUTY in BLACKNESS is revolutionary!! #ShareTheMicNow
